name: Caught In The Rain
description:
A water droplet is caught in grapevine tendrils on a rainy day.

2020. Nikon D3500, 55-200mm Lens + 68mm Extension Tube

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

This piece is for fundraising to support the efforts to assist the people of Malaysia affected by flooding. #MalaysiaNFT
